OL,7,FThe mother of a woman who was stabbed
OL,8,Fto death while she pushed her baby in
OL,9,Fa pram in Bradford has emotionally
OL,10,Frecalled their final conversation to
OL,11,FITV News.
OL,13,FKulsuma Akter, 27, was stabbed
OL,14,Fmultiple times while walking in the
OL,15,Fcity centre on Saturday, alongside her
OL,16,Ffive-month-old son.
OL,18,FToday Habibur Masum, 25, appeared at
OL,19,FBradford Magistrates Court charged
OL,20,Fwith her murder.
