OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV News in Bangladesh,
OL,8,FKulsuma's mother said: "I don't want
OL,9,Fanything else, I just want a true
OL,10,Fjudgement for my child ... no other
OL,11,Fmum should suffer like me, no child
OL,12,Fshould be taken away from their mum."
OL,14,FKulsuma's baby is safe and was not
OL,15,Fharmed in the incident, police said.
OL,17,FThe grandmother, who lives in
OL,18,FBangladesh, said: "On the day she died
OL,19,FI was praying, I didn't talk to her.
