OL,7,F"I spoke to her the day before at
OL,8,FSehri time (when Muslims observing
OL,9,FRamadan will eat before fasting, just
OL,10,Fbefore dawn).
OL,12,F"We exchanged pleasantries. My
OL,13,Fgrandchild was in her arms my
OL,14,Fgrandchild wanted to come to me.
OL,16,F"After which my grandchild was crying
OL,17,Floads that they want to come to me. So
OL,18,Fshe said mum let me put the phone down
OL,19,Fand also it's time to eat.
