OL,7,F"That was the last time I spoke to
OL,8,Fher."
OL,10,FShe says Ms Akter was her youngest
OL,11,Fdaughter who "always looked after her."
OL,13,F"I loved my daughter. I want a
OL,14,Fjudgement," she said through tears.
OL,16,FMasum, of Leamington Avenue, Burnley,
OL,17,Fis also charged with possession of a
OL,18,Fbladed article.
