OL,7,FWearing a grey sweatshirt and flanked
OL,8,Fby two dock officers he spoke only to
OL,9,Fconfirm his name and date of birth.
OL,11,FHe was sent to Bradford Crown Court
OL,12,Ffor a hearing and was remanded in
OL,13,Fcustody by District Judge Alex Boyd.
OL,15,FMr Masum was arrested in Aylesbury,
OL,16,FBuckinghamshire, in the early hours of
OL,17,FTuesday.
